to the navigation ﬁlter’s dynamics model. Biases a↵ecting the IMU data usually must be

estimated by the ﬁlter. Thresholding the IMU accelerations is also usually necessary to

avoid the introduction of unﬁltered IMU noise into the ﬁlter state propagation. Chapter 6

